r jet-break like steeping until at least 21 days post-burst\nsuggests a beaming corrected energy release of E_gamma>3.5x10^52erg, indicating\nthat GRB090926A may have been one of the most energetic bursts ever detected.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2010 17:58:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Jul 2010 08:40:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-09"}
