 show\nresults for the minimal AMSB model, as well as for the hypercharged and gaugino\nAMSB models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Apr 2010 20:19:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Jun 2010 10:31:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
